    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.100" end="00:00:08.720" tts:direction="ltr">Hello, visitors. This is a short lecture
<br />on why we visualize data.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:08.720" end="00:00:11.440" tts:direction="ltr">Why data visualization, why take this
<br />course,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:11.440" end="00:00:14.320" tts:direction="ltr">besides the fact that it's part of</p>
        <p begin="00:00:14.320" end="00:00:19.440" tts:direction="ltr">maybe your graduation requirements or
<br />you've been interested in visualization.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:19.440" end="00:00:22.620" tts:direction="ltr">Well, I'm here to tell you that this is</p>
        <p begin="00:00:22.620" end="00:00:25.340" tts:direction="ltr">an important market ready skill to be able</p>
        <p begin="00:00:25.340" end="00:00:29.460" tts:direction="ltr">to do great things in the 21st century.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:29.460" end="00:00:34.500" tts:direction="ltr">Let's go ahead and talk first about all of
<br />the data that we're collecting.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:34.500" end="00:00:37.180" tts:direction="ltr">We know that data governs</p>
        <p begin="00:00:37.180" end="00:00:40.970" tts:direction="ltr">our world and that we are constantly
<br />collecting data.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:40.970" end="00:00:43.580" tts:direction="ltr">Here's something that though I want you to
<br />remember is that</p>
        <p begin="00:00:43.580" end="00:00:47.160" tts:direction="ltr">all data starts with a human first.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:47.160" end="00:00:50.540" tts:direction="ltr">A human writes an algorithm to collect
<br />data.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:50.540" end="00:00:54.760" tts:direction="ltr">A human creates a way to collect data from
<br />touch</p>
        <p begin="00:00:54.760" end="00:01:00.000" tts:direction="ltr">or from the weather or from the
<br />perspiration that we have.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:00.000" end="00:01:02.220" tts:direction="ltr">It all starts with a human,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:02.220" end="00:01:05.040" tts:direction="ltr">and even though it feels very</p>
        <p begin="00:01:05.290" end="00:01:11.410" tts:direction="ltr">distant maybe and maybe not warm and fuzzy
<br />like maybe a human could be,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:11.410" end="00:01:13.970" tts:direction="ltr">but it really does start with us.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:13.970" end="00:01:17.350" tts:direction="ltr">It's human center data.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:17.350" end="00:01:20.210" tts:direction="ltr">We are able to gather all of this now</p>
        <p begin="00:01:20.210" end="00:01:23.410" tts:direction="ltr">through the vehicles that we drive and we
<br />can</p>
        <p begin="00:01:23.410" end="00:01:29.810" tts:direction="ltr">figure out if we should avoid certain
<br />areas or to prepare for traffic on I 15.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:29.810" end="00:01:33.790" tts:direction="ltr">Weather data has been collected for the
<br />very longest.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:33.790" end="00:01:35.770" tts:direction="ltr">We've always been interested in the
<br />weather</p>
        <p begin="00:01:35.770" end="00:01:38.570" tts:direction="ltr">because of the crops and the food that we
<br />require.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:38.570" end="00:01:41.790" tts:direction="ltr">When we're at the gym, we want to know how
<br />many steps we have,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:41.790" end="00:01:46.245" tts:direction="ltr">what are heartbeats, how many calories
<br />we're exerting.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:46.245" end="00:01:48.820" tts:direction="ltr">These are all just really small tips</p>
        <p begin="00:01:48.820" end="00:01:51.280" tts:direction="ltr">of the iceberg because when it comes to
<br />businesses,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:51.280" end="00:01:54.040" tts:direction="ltr">we are also gathering so many different
<br />data points</p>
        <p begin="00:01:54.040" end="00:01:56.960" tts:direction="ltr">to better inform our decision making.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:56.960" end="00:01:59.680" tts:direction="ltr">As humans, we're gathering this data,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:59.680" end="00:02:03.320" tts:direction="ltr">and it is all around us, as you well know.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:03.320" end="00:02:05.460" tts:direction="ltr">Now, I wanted to share with you</p>
        <p begin="00:02:05.460" end="00:02:12.895" tts:direction="ltr">one tool that I came across when it came
<br />to visualizing some data.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:12.895" end="00:02:17.730" tts:direction="ltr">Here you can follow along by going to the
<br />URL.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:17.730" end="00:02:22.290" tts:direction="ltr">There is a baby name visualizer.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:22.290" end="00:02:26.130" tts:direction="ltr">It goes from 18 80 all the way to 2020</p>
        <p begin="00:02:26.130" end="00:02:31.630" tts:direction="ltr">and provides a visualization of your name.</p>
